  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to KDELibs4Support</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KDELibs4Support</application> package contains libraries
      and utilities to ease the transition from kdelibs 4 to KDE Frameworks 5.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

