    <para>
      <parameter>-DDBUS_INTERFACES_INSTALL_DIR=/usr/share/dbus-1/interfaces</parameter>:
      This switch is used to ensure that <application>D-Bus</application> interfaces
      files are installed in the correct location.
    </para>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
